{"lemma":"غُرُورِ","slug":"غُرُورِ","root":"غ.ر.ر","root_slug":"غ-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ر-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غُرُور","root":"غرر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":9},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31592","n31593"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَرَّ (ḡarra) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cockiness, vanity, pretension"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"deception, delusion","examples":[{"text":"وَمَا يَعِدُهُمُ الشَّيْطَانُ إِلَّا غُرُورًا","english":"Truly Satan promises them nothing but delusion."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of غَرَّ (ḡarra)."},"ipa":["/ɣu.ruːr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31592","headword_ar":"غَرُورٌ","root":"gr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Very deceitful;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied in this sense as an epithet to the present world; (Msb;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what deceives one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) such as a man, and a devil, or other thing; (As, TA;) or such as property or wealth, and rank or station, and desire, and a devil: (B, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guruwrN","text_ar":"غُرُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing by which one is deceived,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of worldly goods or advantages: (S:) or the former signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"devil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"specially; (Yaakoob, S, K;) because he deceives men by false promises and by inspiring hopes; or because he urges a man to do those things which are causes of his being loved but which are followed by that which grieves him: (TA:) and this last sense it has, accord. to ISk, in the Kur xxxi. 33 and xxxv. 5: (S:) also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"present world;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) as an epithet in which the quality of a subst. predominates: and this sense is assigned to it by some as used in the passages of the Kur-án to which reference has just been made. (TA.) [It is masc. and fem., agreeably with analogy.]       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A medicine with which one gargles:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) a word similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laduwdN","text_ar":"لَدُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laEuwqN","text_ar":"لَعُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saEuwTN","text_ar":"سَعُوطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safuwfN","text_ar":"سَفُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["B","TA","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n31593","headword_ar":"غُرُورٌ","root":"gr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"False,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vain, things; vanities:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, K:) as though pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gar~N","text_ar":"غَرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gar~ahu","text_ar":"غَرَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Zj:) or pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAr~N","text_ar":"غَارٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Zj, K;) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uhuwdN","text_ar":"شُهُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAhidN","text_ar":"شَاهِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quEuwdN","text_ar":"قُعُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAEidN","text_ar":"قَاعِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Zj:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is false,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vain; a deception; a thing by which one is deceived."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garuwrN","text_ar":"غَرُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Zj","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}